      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我先梳理一下调用关系。用户通过SchedulerApp来操作，Event和Reminder是领域对象，分别由EventDAO和ReminderService来持久化。这里EventDAO和ReminderService都是部署在CloudNative K8sCluster上的对吧？",
